title: 10 year poro profile icon
body: I dont know why but when everyone got the riot kayle and the poro icon i only got riot kayle. Im just curios why i didnt get the icon but i got riot kayle

replies.body: Everyone has not gotten their gifts yet!  There are a lot of accounts, so it's going to take some time before everyone has received their goodies.  Bookmark the [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-) for updates as we roll out the gifts.  Hang tight!
